      "description": "Available is a 2004 BMW M3 (E46) finished in Carbon Black, featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six power plant and a tactile 6-speed manual gearbox. This example exhibits the linear power delivery and sharp throttle response characteristic of its individual throttle bodies. The chassis is structurally sound, having undergone rear subframe reinforcement\u2014a vital upgrade for this platform. Mechanical highlights include a documented VANOS overhaul and recent valve clearance adjustment, ensuring the double-VANOS system operates with precision. The suspension retains its factory-tuned damping profile, complemented by a limited-slip differential that provides excellent corner-exit traction. While the exterior shows minor road wear consistent with enthusiast use, the drivetrain and underpinnings are sorted and ready for spirited driving.",
